title: Riot girl tristana
body: I was wondering why I did not recieve the skin after liking the facebook page.

replies.body:
Sorry, sometimes the redemption process breaks. We can reunite you with Riot Girl Tristana if you reach out in a [support ticket.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) 

Let me know if you have any questions.
